                        <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18460817-1596-offence-1 t18460817-geo-6"></join>Christchurch</placeName>, and stealing 2 brooches, value 13<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; and 1 seal, 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; his property.</rs>
